hopobject.body: How much does the job pay? zyprexa 10 mg nedir Patton is sweetly game, when she's not clopping through airports scrambling to make her next manufactured meet-cute. And Brody and Scott have a fun, funny chemistry that provokes chuckles despite oneself. But for a chick flick that meets the first two criteria of the Bechdel Test (it has at least two women who talk to each other), "Baggage Claim" fails the third (about something besides a man) big time.
